trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of toolbox items.
trans-unit.target: 表示工具箱項目的集合。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref> class using the specified array of toolbox items.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref>類別使用的工具箱項目指定的陣列。

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> containing the toolbox items to fill the collection with.
trans-unit.target: 類型的陣列<xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>包含工具箱項目的填入集合。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref> class using the specified collection.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref>類別使用指定的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItemCollection"></xref> to fill the new collection with.
Indicates whether the collection contains the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 指出集合是否包含指定<xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> to search the collection for.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the collection contains the specified object; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果集合包含指定的物件，否則， <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to the specified array beginning with the specified destination index.
trans-unit.target: 將集合複製到與指定的目的索引開始的指定的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The index to begin copying to.
Gets the index of the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref>, if it exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得指定的索引<xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>，如果它存在集合中。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> to get the index of in the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>集合中取得的索引。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> at the specified index.
The index of the object to get or set.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定物件的索引。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"></xref> at each valid index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem"> </xref>在每個集合中的有效索引。
